  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Continued support to displacement affected populations of the Syrian crisis</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In Syria NRC will provide emergency shelter solutions for 2,100 households in informal/planned settlements or camps as well as provision of shelter solutions to 500 households and emergency rehabilitation in collective centres/unfinished houses/host family houses. Improvement of infrastructure such as WASH facilities, levelling, communal lighting and gravelling will support IDPs in established settlements/camps and communities.</narrative>
